(Turing machine that acceps 0^n 1^n : n >= 1)

q0:
    read 0 -> write x
              move right
              state q1
    read y -> move right
              state q3

q1:
    read 0 -> move right
    read y -> move right
    read 1 -> write y
              move left
              state q2

q2:
    read y -> move left
    read 0 -> move left
    read x -> move right
              state q0

q3: Can add labels/comments after the colon
    read y -> move right
    read _ -> accept!
    read b -> accept!
